room_title: Escape room "Curse of Dracula: Destroy the Vampire!" by Escape Adventures in Baltimore
room_description: Transylvania, 1893. Famed vampire hunter Abraham Van Helsing has disappeared. The local police have dispatched you and your comrades to investigate his last known whereabouts - Castle Dracula! The sun will set in one hour, and before then you must rescue Van Helsing and destroy Dracula himself if you are to end the curse!
